IDK-Framework

Most used IDK (www.idako.us) classes, starting from base to shape a little growing Framework.

It's not recommended to public use for now, but it is released as open source under a MIT-license style, see LICENSE to know more about that.


CLASSES
=======

 * IDKCore.class.php - Partially implemented, for now: properties 100% implemented, events coming soon. [0.6]
 * IDKDatabase.class.php - Functional [0.9]
 * IDKFactory.class.php - Fast factory pattern implemented [0.8]
 * IDKLog.class.php - [1.0]


~vg